column13: Educational book Optical Coherence Tomography of Ocular Diseases provided at Hawaiian Eye at the Zeiss Symposium for Clinical Dimensions in Glaucoma Diagnostics on January 20 2015

Physicians are provided modest meals during the course of doing business with Carl Zeiss Meditec Inc. The physician could be attending or presenting at an educational presentation, a product training session or being invited for a meal to provide feedback on our products. The total cost of meals are averaged across attendees. This meal took place at Hawaiian Eye ZEISS Symposium for Clinical Dimensions in Glaucoma Diagnostics on January 20 2015
